{"tid":910941,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有些人，在心底從來沒忘記","createTime":"2018-11-21T13:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T11:25:02.000Z","uid":134404,"like":66,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc37aee356c715db975e9cd1b98940436623a37","tid":910941,"uid":134404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"如果有一日，<br />\n大家同你地既伴侶一齊耐咗<br />\n過咗熱戀期，<br />\n因為呢個原因想分手的話<br />\n我希望大家可以好好諗下<br />\n當初點解你會追佢？<br />\n你點解又接受佢呢？<br />\n<br />\n無錯，新鮮感係好吸引<br />\n係你地暫時失去既野<br />\n但如果因爲冇晒新鮮感<br />\n對得耐，所以悶、厭倦<br />\n如果因為咁樣而分開<br />\n你地一定會後悔<br />\n<br />\n我係過來人，我好後悔因爲咁離開我ex<br />\n每日以淚洗面<br />\n每日諗番起同佢所發生既所有事。<br />\n好痛苦<br />\n<br />\n如果愛 可以重來<br />\n我會為你放棄一切<br />\n<br />\n希望大家因爲悶、冇晒新鮮感既時候<br />\n諗下大家曾經有過既開心時光<br />\n既然都一齊左咁耐<br />\n面對過咁多問題<br />\n仲有d咩係overcome唔到<br />\n<br />\n好好珍惜你地既另一半<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 199999<br />\n<br />\n我仲可以用兩年時間 追番你嗎？"},{"pid":"67389526a294730dfe07d92e60dd8f9f6c9fdefb","tid":910941,"uid":169381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:50:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"864e1186d61f176cc6d694bcc307823213f494eb","tid":910941,"uid":134404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67389526a294730dfe07d92e60dd8f9f6c9fdefb","tid":910941,"uid":169381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:50:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:51:06.000Z","msg":"可惜我係宜家先識咁諗"},{"pid":"68cfc78b23da1d64c98b8504ffa48a127c0a2ae1","tid":910941,"uid":114720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:51:43.000Z","msg":"我已經發生緊...情況完住同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cla